conclusion.electoral-propaganda-analysis:
This post constitutes electoral propaganda, but primarily for parliamentary elections, which are still in their legal campaign period. The mention of Ludovic Orban is in the context of his past governmental role, not his presidential candidacy. The post focuses on parliamentary candidates and their economic proposals.
Pros for violation: - Contains CMF number - Is paid electoral content - Mentions a presidential candidate
